    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately not assessed per MRL 2 scoping. Validation evidence demonstrates hemolysis index predictions within 11% of experimental measurements across all COU operating points. The model inputs dataset predates the February 2026 model revision; re-validation of input traceability against the updated geometry is planned for the next scheduled assessment cycle and is considered acceptable under current engineering judgment given the bounded sensitivity results. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
